      <para id="id1169670728095">Have a careful look at the cartoon above. We have to help this poor bald lion enjoy his 21<sup>st</sup> birthday!</para>
      <para id="id1169670680569">Do you have a solution to the lion's problem? In the space provided below, write a humorous solution to this story.</para>
      <para id="id1169670112068">Complete the following checklist:</para>
      <table id="id1169675246375" summary="">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colnum="1" colname="c1"/>
          <colspec colnum="2" colname="c2"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry>I have checked:</entry>
              <entry>
                <emphasis effect="bold"></emphasis>
                <emphasis effect="bold"> Tick</emphasis>
              </entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>
                <list id="id1169670680743" list-type="bulleted">
                  <item>spelling.</item>
                </list>
              </entry>
              <entry/>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>
                <list id="id7443841" list-type="bulleted">
                  <item>punctuation.</item>
                </list>
              </entry>
              <entry/>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>
                <list id="id1169671962737" list-type="bulleted">
                  <item>my work to make sure it is logical, original and interesting.</item>
                </list>
              </entry>
              <entry/>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </table>
